episode: I cannot wait for Easter this Sunday. I get to be with family.

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I cannot wait for Easter this Sunday. I get to be with family.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: That sounds lovely! Family time is the best.

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: Yes it is, Our family always get together on Easter at my Dad's land in the country

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Sounds like a nice tradition!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: We barbecue, sit outdoors and talk, fish and shoot guns

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Sounds like a fun outdoor celebration!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: Plus I anticipating to see the new member of our family. My nephew's baby who was born back in December

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: A new baby in the family is always exciting!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: It has been about 15 year since the last new baby in our family

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: A long time, I'm sure it's a big deal then!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: Holidays are always better when you have kids around.

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: They bring so much energy and joy!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I know. All my nephews are adults, I love them, but I miss when they were kids

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: Nostalgic for the good old days, huh?

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: yes, but you cannot look back, only ahead

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: New memories to be made with the new little one!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: we will have new memoris

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: That's the best part!

dialogue.speaker: Human
dialogue.message: I cannot no wait for Sunday

dialogue.speaker: Bot
dialogue.message: The countdown begins!
